Third-Party Components
======================

Detection & Classification Models
----------------------------------
WatchMyBirds downloads AI models at runtime for object detection and species
classification. These models are NOT part of this project and are licensed
separately by their respective authors. Refer to the upstream model
repositories for applicable license terms before redistribution.


